356
00:18:08,830 --> 00:18:10,240
It's like me and Beiming,

357
00:18:10,280 --> 00:18:11,530
and Constable Zhong.

358
00:18:12,350 --> 00:18:13,960
They once suspected me,

359
00:18:14,310 --> 00:18:16,160
