363
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:23,890
The case of my parents

364
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,390
has been solved.

365
00:18:26,350 --> 00:18:27,440
I actually hope to become

366
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:28,500
