442
00:22:13,160 --> 00:22:13,590
I know!

443
00:22:13,620 --> 00:22:14,770
I didn't steal the Yin-Yang Book!

444
00:22:14,770 --> 00:22:15,570
I believe you

445
00:22:15,590 --> 00:22:17,120
