00:22:42,850 --> 00:22:44,480
But I'm from Poison Valley.

462
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,200
Does that matter?

463
00:22:53,550 --> 00:22:54,480
Thank you.

464
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:58,900
Thank you.

